desc: Honolua Ukuleles is an online Canadian Shop that sells a variety of ukuleles made from beautiful, Eco-conscious tonewoods. Our ukuleles are packed with value and include free extras to help you learn to play. We plant a tree for every ukulele sold. Free shipping throughout North America!

layout.text: Ukuleles designed to be instruments, not toys.
With premium features included in every model, we build for the beginner, the expert, and everyone in-between.
